[Another painful 15 minutes to endure]

3385
01:48:26,520 --> 01:48:30,160
[Tay successfully escapes again]

3386
01:48:26,900 --> 01:48:27,700
Time's up.

3387
01:48:28,420 --> 01:48:29,900
The target has changed.

3388
01:48:30,980 --> 01:48:32,980
The next target is

3389
01:48:34,100 --> 01:48:34,900
Ink.

3390
01:48:35,340 --> 01:48:37,340
The next target is

3391
01:48:37,340 --> 01:48:38,140
Ink.

3392
01:48:38,120 --> 01:48:41,680
[Ink couldn't find the whistle
and becomes the target]

3393
01:48:42,180 --> 01:48:43,580
Ink: Where should I hide?

3394
01:48:46,180 --> 01:48:46,700
Phuak: Where is she?

3395
01:48:46,440 --> 01:48:49,320
[Phuak is spotted
through a mirror reflection]

3396
01:48:46,700 --> 01:48:48,100
Ink: Where should I hide?

3397
01:48:49,800 --> 01:48:52,160
[Phuak also spots Ink running away]

3398
01:48:50,100 --> 01:48:51,700
Phuak: There! There! There!

3399
01:48:52,920 --> 01:48:57,400
[Running for her life]

3400
01:48:55,140 --> 01:48:56,470
Ink: Stop bothering me!

3401
01:48:57,740 --> 01:48:58,820
Ink: Tay, grab Phuak!

3402
01:48:58,040 --> 01:49:00,920
[Phuak quickly catches up]

3403
01:49:02,120 --> 01:49:05,880
[Falls to the ground, desperately
protecting her name tag]

3404
01:49:03,020 --> 01:49:04,220
Phuak: Stop running.

3405
01:49:04,380 --> 01:49:05,700
Ink: I hate you, Phuak.

3406
01:49:06,100 --> 01:49:07,180
Phuak: Stop running.

3407
01:49:07,180 --> 01:49:09,180
Tay: Why didn't you run faster?

3408
01:49:09,180 --> 01:49:09,580
Phuak: Exactly.

3409
01:49:09,580 --> 01:49:11,100
Phuak: You're going to get caught anyway, Ink.

3410
01:49:11,100 --> 01:49:12,830
Tay: Why didn't you run faster?

3411
01:49:14,220 --> 01:49:15,900
Phuak: Flip her over—slowly, slowly.

3412
01:49:15,900 --> 01:49:17,220
Phuak: Tay, Tay—help flip her over.

3413
01:49:17,220 --> 01:49:18,620
Phuak: I can tear it myself in a bit.

3414
01:49:18,620 --> 01:49:19,460
Phuak: Careful, it might hurt.

3415
01:49:19,460 --> 01:49:20,500
Tay: Come on—snake god reincarnated.

3416
01:49:20,500 --> 01:49:21,500
Phuak: Mm, mm, mm.

3417
01:49:23,180 --> 01:49:24,380
Tay: Girl… I'm sorry.

3418
01:49:25,580 --> 01:49:27,380
Tay: We're going down peacefully.

3419
01:49:26,400 --> 01:49:30,120
[They had clearly promised
to protect each other]

3420
01:49:27,380 --> 01:49:28,300
Ink: We… we'll give up together.

3421
01:49:28,300 --> 01:49:28,940
Tay: Just give up.

3422
01:49:28,940 --> 01:49:29,940
Ink: Because we're… today we're...

3423
01:49:29,940 --> 01:49:30,780
Tay: Teammates.

3424
01:49:30,780 --> 01:49:32,910
Ink: Then let's be teammates for once.

3425
01:49:33,220 --> 01:49:34,420
Tay: Girl… I'm sorry.

3426
01:49:43,560 --> 01:49:46,960
[Ink has been eliminated]

3427
01:49:43,820 --> 01:49:45,260
Ink is out.

3428
01:49:46,180 --> 01:49:47,420
Ink is out.

3429
01:49:48,180 --> 01:49:51,020
To compete for the sole heir position,

3430
01:49:51,500 --> 01:49:52,940
Tay and Phuak

3431
01:49:51,720 --> 01:49:58,440
[Phuak vs Tay — the final showdown]

3432
01:49:52,940 --> 01:49:56,460
now begins
the 1-on-1 name tag battle.

3433
01:49:59,020 --> 01:49:59,820
Phuak: A one-on-one, huh.

3434
01:49:59,160 --> 01:50:00,760
[1 vs 1]

3435
01:50:01,520 --> 01:50:05,280
[Entering the final heir selection round]

3436
01:50:07,920 --> 01:50:11,680
[Another challenger eager to claim victory]

3437
01:50:14,360 --> 01:50:16,520
[For the heir position of the R Group]

3438
01:50:19,040 --> 01:50:21,240
[A head-on clash between the two]

3439
01:50:23,200 --> 01:50:26,520
[The ultimate duel to crown the one true winner]

3440
01:50:27,900 --> 01:50:31,600
Phuak: Feels like Goku
taking off his weighted training gear—so light.

3441
01:50:31,600 --> 01:50:34,960
[Why take off the gloves?]

3442
01:50:39,500 --> 01:50:40,340
Tay: Phuak.

3443
01:50:40,940 --> 01:50:42,000
Phuak: Bring it on.

3444
01:50:42,060 --> 01:50:43,790
Phuak: Let's settle this, Tay.

3445
01:50:48,700 --> 01:50:51,300
Phuak: Hey—Tay,
don't squeeze my hand so hard!

3446
01:50:57,560 --> 01:51:00,920
[Tay adopts a "lying flat" battle strategy]

3447
01:51:02,020 --> 01:51:03,820
Tay: Ugh—hey, Phuak.

3448
01:51:10,980 --> 01:51:11,940
Tay: Phuak.

3449
01:51:13,000 --> 01:51:15,720
[Tay tries to bite again]

3450
01:51:15,540 --> 01:51:16,600
Phuak: Don't bite!

3451
01:51:16,860 --> 01:51:18,860
Phuak: What are you, a human or a dog?

3452
01:51:23,040 --> 01:51:25,280
[Grabs Tay's name tag]

3453
01:51:29,200 --> 01:51:31,440
[Grabs Phuak's name tag]

3454
01:51:34,320 --> 01:51:37,560
[Who will become the final heir?]

3455
01:51:40,480 --> 01:51:43,640
[Royal Cliff Grand Hotel]

3456
01:51:43,800 --> 01:51:46,520
[Rip—!]

3457
01:51:47,580 --> 01:51:51,580
PD: Alright, the name tag ripping mission
has successfully concluded.

3458
01:51:54,180 --> 01:51:56,180
Oat: I don't really care who won.

3459
01:51:56,180 --> 01:51:58,100
Oat: I just want to know who took me out.

3460
01:51:58,100 --> 01:51:59,300
Jeff: Who was it, bro?

3461
01:51:59,300 --> 01:52:00,160
Ink: Who did it?

3462
01:52:02,580 --> 01:52:03,860
Jeff: These are Phuak's finger guards.

3463
01:52:03,860 --> 01:52:04,420
Oat: One.

3464
01:52:05,420 --> 01:52:06,100
Oat: Here.

3465
01:52:06,100 --> 01:52:06,660
Oat: Two.

3466
01:52:07,620 --> 01:52:08,300
Oat: Three.

3467
01:52:08,300 --> 01:52:09,500
Jeff: There are 5 of them?

3468
01:52:09,500 --> 01:52:10,300
Oat: Four.

3469
01:52:10,940 --> 01:52:11,500
Oat: Five.

3470
01:52:11,500 --> 01:52:12,220
Ink: Five finger guards?

3471
01:52:11,720 --> 01:52:14,920
[Five finger guards scattered on the ground]

3472
01:52:12,220 --> 01:52:13,700
Jeff: Are all five here?

3473
01:52:13,700 --> 01:52:16,300
Oat: I don't know who inherited the fortune,
but I know who took me out.

3474
01:52:16,300 --> 01:52:18,180
Oat: Because there's only one truth.

3475
01:52:18,180 --> 01:52:20,180
Ink: Tsk tsk, adding drama now, huh.

3476
01:52:23,900 --> 01:52:25,230
Ink: Really milking it.

3477
01:52:25,660 --> 01:52:26,590
Ink: Seriously.

3478
01:52:27,220 --> 01:52:28,280
Oat: Oh wow, oh wow.

3479
01:52:28,940 --> 01:52:30,140
Phuak: Found the finger guards.

3480
01:52:30,140 --> 01:52:30,670
Oat: Tch.

3481
01:52:31,140 --> 01:52:32,100
Oat: How could you not?

3482
01:52:32,100 --> 01:52:34,230
Oat: They were all stuck to my name tag.

3483
01:52:34,620 --> 01:52:35,740
Phuak: Stuck to the Velcro?

3484
01:52:35,740 --> 01:52:36,580
Oat: All of them stuck there.

3485
01:52:36,580 --> 01:52:38,420
Phuak: No wonder I searched forever.

3486
01:52:38,420 --> 01:52:39,220
Offroad: I really want to know the result.

3487
01:52:39,220 --> 01:52:40,700
Mos: But look at these clothes…

3488
01:52:40,700 --> 01:52:42,620
Mos: Look at them—completely wrecked.

3489
01:52:42,620 --> 01:52:43,700
Mos: Tay.

3490
01:52:43,700 --> 01:52:45,020
PD: Time to reveal the answer.

3491
01:52:44,280 --> 01:52:47,520
[Phuak and Tay—
their clothes are completely torn up]

3492
01:52:46,140 --> 01:52:47,200
Offroad: Is it Tay?

3493
01:52:49,080 --> 01:52:53,840
[Who is the heir of the R Group?]

3494
01:52:57,580 --> 01:52:58,900
PD: 1, 2, 3.

3495
01:52:58,520 --> 01:53:03,680
[Now revealing the answer]

3496
01:53:06,280 --> 01:53:08,880
[Phuak made the first move]

3497
01:53:09,760 --> 01:53:12,720
[Tay launched a fierce counterattack]

3498
01:53:17,840 --> 01:53:20,760
[Phuak's name tag slipped
to his shoulder]

3499
01:53:24,680 --> 01:53:27,600
[Tay fought to the very end, refusing to let go]

3500
01:53:28,340 --> 01:53:29,940
Phuak: Why are you so strong?

3501
01:53:30,720 --> 01:53:33,680
[Phuak tried his best to defend]

3502
01:53:36,720 --> 01:53:39,680
[Tay went all out]

3503
01:54:07,780 --> 01:54:09,040
Tay: Phuak, I'm sorry.

3504
01:54:09,300 --> 01:54:10,160
Tay: I'm sorry.

3505
01:54:10,620 --> 01:54:11,900
Phuak: As long as you win, it's fine.

3506
01:54:11,900 --> 01:54:14,740
PD: The name tag ripping battle mission is over.

3507
01:54:16,020 --> 01:54:16,820
Phuak: Not bad, not bad.

3508
01:54:16,820 --> 01:54:18,750
Tay: Let's team up again next time.

3509
01:54:26,900 --> 01:54:29,580
Ink: Quiet luxury, quiet luxury.

3510
01:54:29,580 --> 01:54:31,580
Tay: Now you get what "quiet luxury" means?

3511
01:54:31,580 --> 01:54:33,300
Oat: OK. OK.

3512
01:54:32,000 --> 01:54:37,400
[The heir of the R Group is—Tay]

3513
01:54:37,420 --> 01:54:40,080
PD: Tay, please come sign to receive the shares.

3514
01:54:43,100 --> 01:54:45,060
Oat: Today,
we've prepared a special prize for Tay.

3515
01:54:45,060 --> 01:54:47,920
Oat: It's a full night's stay
at that hotel just now.

3516
01:54:48,740 --> 01:54:49,940
Tay: Any witnesses? Who's going to be my witness?

3517
01:54:49,940 --> 01:54:51,300
Jeff: Sure, I can do it.

3518
01:54:51,300 --> 01:54:53,580
Jeff: For the boss, of course no problem.

3519
01:54:53,580 --> 01:54:55,780
Phuak: Since he's taking the shares,
can I have the trophy?

3520
01:54:55,780 --> 01:54:57,780
Tay: Since you're the witness, we will…

3521
01:54:57,780 --> 01:54:59,340
Tay: hand over the entire second floor
to your management.

3522
01:54:57,920 --> 01:55:01,240
[What about my share of the prize money?]

3523
01:54:59,340 --> 01:55:01,580
Jeff: Thank you so much.
It's truly an honor.

3524
01:55:01,580 --> 01:55:04,220
Jeff: Good thing I've always
been on good terms with Tay.

3525
01:55:04,220 --> 01:55:05,420
Oat: That's not ours.

3526
01:55:06,700 --> 01:55:08,500
Phuak: Wait. You already took the shares.

3527
01:55:08,500 --> 01:55:09,860
Phuak: I just want a trophy
to take home and display, okay?

3528
01:55:09,860 --> 01:55:10,300
Oat: That's not ours.

3529
01:55:10,300 --> 01:55:10,900
Phuak: That's for second place.

3530
01:55:10,900 --> 01:55:11,660
Oat: No need, no need, no need.

3531
01:55:10,920 --> 01:55:14,840
[Looking especially cute today]

3532
01:55:11,660 --> 01:55:13,320
Phuak: It's for second place!

3533
01:55:14,900 --> 01:55:19,060
Tay: Alright, please stay tuned to
Running Man Thailand. Never Stop Running.

3534
01:55:19,060 --> 01:55:23,220
Every Sunday at 8 PM, exclusively on the iQIYI app
and iQ.com.

3535
01:55:26,700 --> 01:55:30,700
Running Man Thailand — Never Stop Running!

3536
01:55:36,980 --> 01:55:37,980
Ink: Where are we?

3537
01:55:38,980 --> 01:55:39,620
Phuak: Oh man…

3538
01:55:39,620 --> 01:55:41,380
PD: An Earthling has infiltrated

3539
01:55:41,380 --> 01:55:46,340
PD: to stop the aliens
from returning to their home planet.

3540
01:55:48,020 --> 01:55:49,220
Phuak: I can't hold on anymore.
